{"tid":2354284,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"20 歲售貨員被指藏士巴拿螺絲批　警認未睹特別行為　但「佢見到我轉身跑走」","createTime":"2021-01-05T11:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T14:03:29.000Z","uid":56115,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"49da92102591492b2b2b747fdcda61070e990eed","tid":2354284,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T11:02:35.000Z","msg":"網民前年 11 月 11 日發起「三罷」，20 歲售貨員被指在上水天平山村藏有士巴拿、螺絲批及對講機，承認無牌管有無線電通訊器具罪，否認藏有非法工具，今（5 日）在粉嶺裁判法院受審。警員葉浩偉在盤問下承認，沒有看到被告做特別行為，惟指他逃走，「佢見到我轉身跑走，叫佢唔好走仲走」。辯方指當時葉以便裝當值，被告未必知道其警員身份；葉則指自己與軍裝警員同行。案件押後至 2 月 5 日裁決，被告期間以原有條件保釋。<br />\n<br />\n警僅因被告轉身逃走而覺可疑<br />\n<br />\n葉在盤問下承認，該批穿著深色衣物的人士只是拿著長傘、沒有做實際行為，亦沒有人拿著士巴拿等物品。"},{"pid":"e946d18391174b947c212fcf9a6e7c182147cf94","tid":2354284,"uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T11:02:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/20-%E6%AD%B2%E5%94%AE%E8%B2%A8%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%97%8F%E5%A3%AB%E5%B7%B4%E6%8B%BF%E8%9E%BA%E7%B5%B2%E6%89%B9-%E8%AD%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%9C%AA%E7%9D%B9%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-%E4%BD%86-%E4%BD%A2%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E8%BD%89%E8%BA%AB%E8%B7%91%E8%B5%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F20-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%2594%25AE%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E6%258B%25BF%25E8%259E%25BA%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E6%2589%25B9-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%259C%25AA%25E7%259D%25B9%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%2588%25A5%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E4%25BD%2586-%25E4%25BD%25A2%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%2588%2591%25E8%25BD%2589%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E8%25B7%2591%25E8%25B5%25B0%2F&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=5f098dec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F20-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%2594%25AE%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%25A3%25A